rules:
Welcome to The Doofus Squad

Rules to follow:

1. Don't impersonate staff (will be removed)

2. Staff must not be blocked

3. NSFW AT YOUR OWN RISK!

4. Keep environment drama-free, handle personal issues privately (staff will warn first, if problem persists you will be removed)

5. Be respectful of others, no Bullying, Harassment, or Discrimination (Staff will warn first, if problem persists you will be removed)

6. No pressuring people to drink or smoke if not interested, we're here to have fun first and foremost! (staff will warn first, if problem persists you will be removed)

7. Drink responsibly, we're all adults here know your limits. We are not responsible for your overconsumption

8. When there's a DJ, don't play music through your mic unless for a drinking song and please move to a secluded area (staff will warn first, if problem persists you will be removed)
